##########
# Win 10 / Server 2016 / Server 2019 Initial Setup Script - zomg turbo preset
# Source: https://github.com/Disassembler0/Win10-Initial-Setup-Script
# Usage:
# From elevated shell:
# powershell.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File Win10.ps1 -include Win10.psm1 -preset Turbo.preset

##########

### Require administrator privileges ###
RequireAdmin

### Privacy Tweaks ###
DisableWiFiSense
DisableAppSuggestions
EnableLocationTracking
DisableAdvertisingID

# Restrict Windows Update P2P delivery optimization to computers in local network - Default since 1703
SetP2PUpdateLocal

### Security Tweaks ###
DisableSMBServer
EnableFirewall
EnableDefender

# Enable Core Isolation Memory Integrity - Part of Windows Defender System Guard virtualization-based security - Applicable since 1803
EnableCIMemoryIntegrity

DisableAutoplay
DisableAutorun

### Service Tweaks ###
EnableFastStartup

### UI Tweaks ###
ShowTaskManagerDetails
ShowSmallTaskbarIcons
SetTaskbarCombineAlways
HideTaskbarPeopleIcon
ShowTrayIcons
HideRecentlyAddedApps

# Adjusts visual effects for performance - Disables animations, transparency etc. but leaves font smoothing and miniatures enabled
SetVisualFXPerformance

SetSoundSchemeNone
DisableStartupSound

### Explorer UI Tweaks ###
ShowKnownExtensions
ShowHiddenFiles


### Application Tweaks ###
UninstallThirdPartyBloat
DisableAdobeFlash
InstallLinuxSubsystem
InstallHyperV

### Unpinning ###
UnpinStartMenuTiles
UnpinTaskbarIcons

### Auxiliary Functions ###
WaitForKey
Restart
